		&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;!-- [Format Time: 0.0055 seconds] --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note that using http link is no longer required, and any configuration options that could be passed to http link can be passed to &lt;code&gt;createUploadLink&lt;/code&gt;. In fact, if http link is used before &lt;code&gt;createUploadLink&lt;/code&gt; file uploads wonâ€™t work at all because http link is a terminal link and the upload link added after would not be used.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now we can upload files to our GraphQL endpoint using &lt;code&gt;Mutation&lt;/code&gt; component.&lt;/p&gt;
